Installation instructions
-------------------------

    1. Install FEniCS 1.x from http://fenicsproject.org/
    2. Install dolfin-adjoint 1.x from http://www.dolfin-adjoint.org/
    3. Install the most recent version of libspud from the Fluidity project https://github.com/FluidityProject/fluidity
    4. Clone this respositroy and include its root path to $PYTHONPATH


Test cases
----------
drag
entrainment
flux input
concentration gradient
erosion
